{"id": "art-2029", "label": "Art. 2029", "title": "Art. 2029: Dreptul de retenţie al mandatarului", "slug": "art-2029", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 2029: Dreptul de reten&#355;ie al mandatarului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>Pentru garantarea tuturor\ncrean&#355;elor sale împotriva mandantului izvorâte din mandat, mandatarul are\nun drept de reten&#355;ie asupra bunurilor primite cu ocazia execut&#259;rii\nmandatului de la mandant ori pe seama acestuia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_622693730\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1088\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_622693730\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>SUBSEC&#354;IUNEA\n3<sup>1</sup>:§3<sup>1</sup>. Dispozi&#355;ii privind mandatul de ocrotire</span></b></p>"}